# Bento Grid Verification Checklist

- [ ] Navigate to http://localhost:3000/vi
- [ ] Observe Bento Grid animation on hover
- [ ] Verify "stunning" factor:
    - [ ] Tapered tail
    - [ ] Vibrant but elegant colors
    - [ ] "Inner bloom" effect
- [ ] Verify technical stability:
    - [ ] No blue light bleed at margins
    - [ ] Perfect corner handling (rounded-3xl)
    - [ ] Smooth performance (60fps feel)
- [ ] Capture final documentation (screenshots/recordings)
